00:44:54.760 --> 00:44:57.400
But the fundamental question,
mutual assured destruction,

00:44:57.400 --> 00:44:59.590
the answer is yes.

00:44:59.590 --> 00:45:02.770
In the case of the US
and the Soviet Union,

00:45:02.770 --> 00:45:05.680
the fact that once we had
each developed arsenals

00:45:05.680 --> 00:45:10.480
so big that after you attack me
and do your best to disarm me,

00:45:10.480 --> 00:45:13.750
