assured destruction.

00:45:16.810 --> 00:45:21.470
And that becomes a fundamental
fact about life for the two

00:45:21.470 --> 00:45:25.540
of us, if we keep it in
mind, and if we deal with it.

00:45:25.540 --> 00:45:29.930
And that's now a fact, not just
in our relations with Russia,

00:45:29.930 --> 00:45:31.960
but in our relations with China.

00:45:31.960 --> 00:45:35.320
Now in the book, I
described this, as if--

00:45:35.320 --> 00:45:37.750
in a grotesque analogy,
but if you think about it--

00:45:37.750 --> 00:45:41.350
it's as if you and I
wake up tomorrow morning,

00:45:41.350 --> 00:45:44.080
and we each have our
head, we have our arms,

00:45:44.080 --> 00:45:46.810
but our backbone and
our respiratory systems

00:45:46.810 --> 00:45:52.360
have been unified.

00:45:52.360 --> 00:45:55.940
And we therefore
are Siamese twins.

00:45:55.940 --> 00:45:59.320
And now you look at me and you
say, well, this guy is evil.

00:45:59.320 --> 00:46:00.490
This guy is dangerous.

00:46:00.490 --> 00:46:02.430
This guy is delirious.

00:46:02.430 --> 00:46:06.840
This guy deserves
to be strangled.

00:46:06.840 --> 00:46:11.610
But then you think about,
well, if I strangle him,

00:46:11.610 --> 00:46:14.560
in the next minute, I will
have committed suicide.

00:46:14.560 --> 00:46:16.820
So it's like a suicide pact.

00:46:16.820 --> 00:46:19.290
But one that you
can't get out of.

00:46:19.290 --> 00:46:23.610
